                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6314" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0196</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8784 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药——“混改”后的崎岖之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yunnan Baiyao - bumpy road after &quot;mixed reform&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李宏彪，陶文俊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药；混合所有制改革；公司治理；经济增加值</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yunnan Baiyao; Mixed ownership reform; Corporate governance; Economic value added</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">基于国家助力国企混合所有制改革（以下简称“混改”）的背景下，且正处在国企改革的关键时期，虽国企混改有所建树，但是行业的异质性让改革步履维艰，而且改革后也存在治理体系和治理能力、组织架构、内部监督制约机制等不完善、不科学的问题。因而，研究经典案例具有一定的价值。本案例描述了云南白药在混改前后发生的事件，从混改动因、混改路径选择、企业治理目标对云南白药开展相关探究，对其发展历程来探索混改前后股权结构变化和对董事会、监事会以及高级管理人员的影响分析，并结合国家政策和内部财务分析探究其混改成果与治理效果。同时提出相关建议，以期为混合所有制改革案例研究提供新的思路，进一步引导学员对案例的思考，对公司治理有一个更深层次的理解。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Based on the background that the state assists the mixed ownership reform of state-owned enterprises (hereinafter referred to as &quot;mixed reform&quot;) and is in the key period of state-owned enterprise reform, although the mixed reform of state-owned enterprises has made achievements, the heterogeneity of the industry makes the reform difficult, and there will be imperfect and unscientific problems such as governance system and governance ability, organizational structure, internal supervision and restriction mechanism after the reform. Therefore, the study of classic cases has a certain value. This case describes the events of Yunnan Baiyao before and after the mixed reform, explores the relevant research of Yunnan Baiyao from the motivation, path selection and corporate governance objectives of the mixed reform, explores the changes of equity structure before and after the mixed reform, analyzes the impact of the board of directors, the board of supervisors and senior managers, and explores its mixed reform results and governance effects in combination with national policies and internal financial analysis. At the same time, relevant suggestions are put forward in order to provide new ideas for the case study of mixed ownership reform, further guide the students to think about the case and have a deeper understanding of corporate governance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混合所有制改革；混合所有制改革路径；股权结构、管理层、激励机制；经济增加值(EVA)</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
